<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <title>Welcome to Shams Suya Spot on SnackGo!</title>
</head>
<body style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; background-color: #f9f9f9; color: #333; margin: 0; padding: 20px;">
    <div style="max-width: 600px; margin: auto; background-color: #fff; padding: 20px; border: 1px solid #eaeaea; border-radius: 8px;">
        <h2 style="color: #ff6600;">Welcome {{vendorName}} {{companyName}}!</h2>
        <p>Dear <strong>{{staffName}}</strong>,</p>

        <p>We are thrilled to have you join our team. To get started, please activate your account by clicking the link below:</p>

        <p style="text-align: center;">
            <a href="{{activationLink}}" style="display: inline-block; padding: 10px 20px; background-color: #800080; color: #fff; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 4px;">Activate Your Account</a>
        </p>

        <p>If you encounter any issues during the activation process, please do not hesitate to reach out to our support team at <a href="mailto:{{supportEmail}}" style="color: #ff6600;">{{supportEmail}}</a> or call us at <span style="color: #ff6600;">{{supportPhone}}</span>.</p>

        <p>We look forward to working with you and making SnackGo the go-to solution for quick and delicious snacks!</p>

        <p>Best regards,</p>
        <p style="color: #800080;"><strong>{{senderName}}</strong><br/>
        SnackGo Team<br/>
        <span style="color: #ff6600;">{{senderContactInfo}}</span></p>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
